-content__image\"><img src=\"../../assets/images/img-works-people-page11.jpg\" alt=\"\"/>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__content\">\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__category\">MR\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"c-works-content__head  c-heading is-xxs\">医療の未来を支え、患者さんへ希望を届ける。\n                        </h3>\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__name\">A.N\n                        </div>\n                      </div></a>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"c-works-content__slider-others-slide  swiper-slide\"><a class=\"c-works-content__card  js-current-nav\" href=\"../../work_people/12/\">\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__image\"><img src=\"../../assets/images/img-works-people-page12.jpg\" alt=\"\"/>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__content\">\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__category\">食品研究職\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"c-works-content__head  c-heading is-xxs\">食の未来を支える、原料研究と価値創造。\n                        </h3>\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__name\">A.K\n                        </div>\n                      </div></a>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"c-works-content__slider-others-slide  swiper-slide\"><a class=\"c-works-content__card  js-current-nav\" href=\"../../work_people/13/\">\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__image\"><img src=\"../../assets/images/img-works-people-page13.jpg\" alt=\"\"/>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"c-works-content__content\">\n                        <div class=\"c-works-content__category\">食品営業職\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"c-works-content__head  c-heading is-xxs\">研究と市場をつなぐ、“価値提案”の最前線。\n                        </h3>\n      